\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?\">Ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube n\u00ean bao g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cach-tao-phan-gioi-thieu-ve-youtube.html\/#Yeu_cau_va_dinh_dang_cho_phan_gioi_thieu_YouTube\" title=\"Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng cho ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube\">Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng cho ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-14\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cach-tao-phan-gioi-thieu-ve-youtube.html\/#Ty_le_khung_hinh\" title=\"T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 khung h\u00ecnh\">T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 khung h\u00ecnh<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-15\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cach-tao-phan-gioi-thieu-ve-youtube.html\/#Dinh_dang_video\" title=\"\u0110\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng video\">\u0110\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng video<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-16\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cach-tao-phan-gioi-thieu-ve-youtube.html\/#Cat_ghep_am_nhac\" title=\"C\u1eaft gh\u00e9p \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c\">C\u1eaft gh\u00e9p \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-17\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cach-tao-phan-gioi-thieu-ve-youtube.html\/#Phan_tao_phan_gioi_thieu_ve_YouTube_nen_dai_bao_lau\" title=\"Ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 YouTube n\u00ean d\u00e0i bao l\u00e2u?\">Ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 YouTube n\u00ean d\u00e0i bao l\u00e2u?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-18\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cach-tao-phan-gioi-thieu-ve-youtube.html\/#Cac_vi_du_gioi_thieu_tren_YouTube_de_truyen_cam_hung_cho_ban\" title=\"C\u00e1c v\u00ed d\u1ee5 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean YouTube \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho b\u1ea1n\">C\u00e1c v\u00ed d\u1ee5 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean YouTube \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho b\u1ea1n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-19\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cach-tao-phan-gioi-thieu-ve-youtube.html\/#Ban_da_san_sang_tao_phan_gioi_thieu_tren_YouTube_chua\" title=\"B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean YouTube ch\u01b0a?\">B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean YouTube ch\u01b0a?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<div class=\"FKBQDbxWDMukLsIbfi4HMw== ICEOPVWfmFh4dcn1bI40Gg==\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"FKBQDbxWDMukLsIbfi4HMw== ICEOPVWfmFh4dcn1bI40Gg==\">\n<div class=\"Rqore-G6w1LwsLlvH7SxWg== Lo1+jREm2t4VJb8Xudn8RA==\">\n<div class=\"G8TJvs9dy2CaHKlP1Nf3vA==\">\n<div class=\"FKBQDbxWDMukLsIbfi4HMw== ICEOPVWfmFh4dcn1bI40Gg==\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 YouTube \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00fang trong ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb video. N\u1ebfu video c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Cho d\u00f9 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o k\u00eanh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh hay t\u0103ng t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem, th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">Blog n\u00e0y xem x\u00e9t t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a video gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch tr\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda video tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Animoto c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u01b0a b\u1ea1n l\u00ean c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 ti\u1ebfp theo.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15165\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15165\" style=\"width: 901px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15165 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1-2.png\" alt=\"Cach-tao-phan-gioi-thieu-ve-youtube\" width=\"901\" height=\"601\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1-2.png 901w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1-2-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1-2-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15165\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 YouTube<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2 class=\"SectionTitle-module--sectionTitle--3wG12 SectionTitle-module--spacing--23XyU\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Phan_gioi_thieu_YouTube_la_gi\"><\/span>Ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/\">YouTube<\/a> l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>T\u1ea1o\u00a0<span class=\"BaseButton-module--fullWidth--1g5Gb\">ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube<\/span>\u00a0hay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem tr\u00ean k\u00eanh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0Ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn s\u01a1 l\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n cho video c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0C\u00e1c \u0111o\u1ea1n d\u1ef1ng phim m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u si\u00eau ng\u1eafn n\u00e0y n\u1eb1m \u1edf ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u (ho\u1eb7c g\u1ea7n \u0111o\u1ea1n phim) c\u1ee7a video YouTube c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0i\u00a0<strong class=\"BoldCopy-module--strong--fdPVR\">t\u1eeb n\u0103m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e2y.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"SectionTitle-module--sectionTitle--3wG12 SectionTitle-module--spacing--23XyU\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tai_sao_nen_tao_phan_gioi_thieu_tren_YouTube\"><\/span>T\u1ea1i sao n\u00ean t\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean YouTube?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>C\u00e1c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y cho th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2022,\u00a0<span class=\"BaseButton-module--fullWidth--1g5Gb\">kho\u1ea3ng 82% l\u01b0u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng truy c\u1eadp tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u<\/span>\u00a0\u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb video, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ch\u1eadm l\u1ea1i.\u00a0Trung b\u00ecnh,\u00a0<span class=\"BaseButton-module--fullWidth--1g5Gb\">1,6 t\u1ef7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e0nh h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 gi\u1edd<\/span>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 xem video tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.\u00a0Ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa vi\u1ec7c khi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ho\u1eb7c thu h\u00fat h\u1ecd theo c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t;\u00a0Ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb video.<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"SectionTitle-module--sectionTitle--3wG12 SectionTitle-module--spacing--23XyU\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_tao_phan_gioi_thieu_YouTube_voi_Animoto_trong_4_buoc\"><\/span>C\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube v\u1edbi Animoto trong 4 b\u01b0\u1edbc<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3 class=\"Label-module--label--3mPBJ Label-module--spacing--2eZ0x\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Chon_mot_mau_video_gioi_thieu_Youtube\"><\/span>1. Ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu video gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u Youtube<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">Duy\u1ec7t qua th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n m\u1eabu c\u1ee7a Animoto v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u\u00a0<span class=\"BaseButton-module--fullWidth--1g5Gb\">suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu n\u00e0o<\/span>\u00a0s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean video gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.\u00a0Nhanh ch\u00f3ng gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed7i video v\u1edbi m\u1eabu n\u00e0y:<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"Label-module--label--3mPBJ Label-module--spacing--2eZ0x\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Tai_len_phuong_tien_cua_ban\"><\/span>2. T\u1ea3i l\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">Sart b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u1ea3i \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 video clip c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00ean Animoto.\u00a0\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean xem th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 video \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1eb5n t\u1eeb Getty Images.\u00a0K\u00e9o v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ea3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o d\u1ef1 \u00e1n.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"Label-module--label--3mPBJ Label-module--spacing--2eZ0x\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Hay_sang_tao\"><\/span>3. H\u00e3y s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">T\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh v\u0103n b\u1ea3n video c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1 t\u00ednh th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\u00a0<span class=\"BaseButton-module--fullWidth--1g5Gb\">ki\u1ec3u v\u0103n b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u video<\/span>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 th\u00eam m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p cho video c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, h\u00e3y th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n nh\u1ea1c t\u1eeb th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u00e0i h\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ph\u00e9p c\u1ee7a Animoto \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a video.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"Label-module--label--3mPBJ Label-module--spacing--2eZ0x\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Kiem_tra_lai\"><\/span>4. Ki\u1ec3m tra l\u1ea1i<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15166\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15166\" style=\"width: 387px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15166 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/2-2.png\" alt=\"Kiem-tra-lai-video\" width=\"387\" height=\"581\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/2-2.png 387w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/2-2-200x300.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 387px) 100vw, 387px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15166\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ki\u1ec3m tra l\u1ea1i video<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">G\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac nh\u1ea5p v\u00e0o n\u00fat &#8216;ph\u00e1t&#8217; \u1edf g\u00f3c d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f9ng b\u00ean tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m tra k\u1ef9 video gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0Khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng, h\u00e3y xu\u1ea5t video c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00eam video gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u video YouTube c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0H\u00e3y nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c\u00a0<strong class=\"BoldCopy-module--strong--fdPVR\">video s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u01b0u v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n trong t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"SectionTitle-module--sectionTitle--3wG12 SectionTitle-module--spacing--23XyU\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_phuong_phap_hay_nhat_ve_phan_gioi_thieu_YouTube\"><\/span>3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p hay nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p hay nh\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n k\u00eanh YouTube c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh:<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"Label-module--label--3mPBJ Label-module--spacing--2eZ0x\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Thuong_hieu_ro_rang_va_nhat_quan\"><\/span>1. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1n<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">YouTube l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch n\u00e2ng cao nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">T\u0103ng t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem. M\u1ed9t k\u00eanh YouTube th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i bao g\u1ed3m bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0ng, \u200b\u200bt\u00ean k\u00eanh, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1n, \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c ho\u1eb7c hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng \u00e2m thanh h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 d\u00f2ng gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. Nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem bi\u1ebft b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m g\u00ec v\u00e0 gi\u00fap <strong class=\"BoldCopy-module--strong--fdPVR\">th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh.\u00a0<\/strong>V\u1edbi g\u00f3i Animoto\u00a0<span class=\"BaseButton-module--fullWidth--1g5Gb\">Professional ho\u1eb7c Professional Plus<\/span>\u00a0, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng\u00a0<span class=\"BaseButton-module--fullWidth--1g5Gb\">Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e3 l\u01b0u<\/span>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ph\u00f4ng ch\u1eef, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"Label-module--label--3mPBJ Label-module--spacing--2eZ0x\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Dung_quen_van_ban_dong\"><\/span>2. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean v\u0103n b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed9ng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">Th\u00eam v\u0103n b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0o ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.\u00a0S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u0103n b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem \u0111\u1ebfn k\u00eanh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb d\u00f2ng gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem d\u1ec5 theo d\u00f5i h\u01a1n.\u00a0Animoto cung c\u1ea5p nhi\u1ec1u\u00a0<span class=\"BaseButton-module--fullWidth--1g5Gb\">ph\u00f4ng ch\u1eef, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u v\u0103n b\u1ea3n<\/span>\u00a0s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"Label-module--label--3mPBJ Label-module--spacing--2eZ0x\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Luon_tuy_chinh\"><\/span>3. Lu\u00f4n t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">Ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">\u00c2m nh\u1ea1c ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/li>\n<li class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">V\u0103n b\u1ea3n ho\u1ea1t h\u00ecnh<\/li>\n<li class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1n l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o k\u00eanh YouTube c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. T\u1ea3i l\u00ean ph\u00f4ng ch\u1eef, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0ng v\u00e0 \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh video gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 class=\"SectionTitle-module--sectionTitle--3wG12 SectionTitle-module--spacing--23XyU\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Phan_gioi_thieu_YouTube_nen_bao_gom_nhung_gi\"><\/span>Ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube n\u00ean bao g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">Ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean YouTube c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i, nh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa vi\u1ec7c th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem ho\u1eb7c b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0o.\u00a0Ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0i t\u1eeb n\u0103m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e2y;\u00a0l\u00e2u h\u01a1n v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, h\u00e3y th\u1eed m\u1eabu t\u1ef1 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t \u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.<\/p>\n<p>Khi n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube, t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1n n\u00ean r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111i \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.\u00a0Tr\u00e1nh ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u;\u00a0ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.\u00a0Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, h\u00e3y nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1n khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0ng, \u200b\u200bd\u00f2ng gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"SectionTitle-module--sectionTitle--3wG12 SectionTitle-module--spacing--23XyU\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Yeu_cau_va_dinh_dang_cho_phan_gioi_thieu_YouTube\"><\/span>Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng cho ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">\u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o video gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.\u00a0D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch ba \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea7n ghi nh\u1edb:<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"Label-module--label--3mPBJ Label-module--spacing--2eZ0x\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ty_le_khung_hinh\"><\/span>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 khung h\u00ecnh<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15167\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15167\" style=\"width: 1710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15167 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/cardmapr-nl-NFCou1VhdjE-unsplash-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Ti-le-khung-hinh\" width=\"1710\" height=\"2560\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/cardmapr-nl-NFCou1VhdjE-unsplash-scaled.jpg 1710w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/cardmapr-nl-NFCou1VhdjE-unsplash-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/cardmapr-nl-NFCou1VhdjE-unsplash-684x1024.jpg 684w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/cardmapr-nl-NFCou1VhdjE-unsplash-768x1150.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/cardmapr-nl-NFCou1VhdjE-unsplash-1026x1536.jpg 1026w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/cardmapr-nl-NFCou1VhdjE-unsplash-1368x2048.jpg 1368w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1710px) 100vw, 1710px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15167\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ec9-l\u1ec7-khung-h\u00ecnh<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 n\u1ed9i dung video tr\u00ean YouTube \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 khung h\u00ecnh \u01b0u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 16: 9.\u00a0\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd l\u00e0 video s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh l\u1ea1i cho \u0111\u00fang k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc.\u00a0Ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi \u0111\u0103ng n\u1ebfu n\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1c.\u00a0Animoto cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc video c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 khung h\u00ecnh ngang, h\u00ecnh vu\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c chi\u1ec1u d\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"Label-module--label--3mPBJ Label-module--spacing--2eZ0x\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dinh_dang_video\"><\/span>\u0110\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng video<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c video gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean YouTube ph\u1ea3i \u1edf\u00a0<strong class=\"BoldCopy-module--strong--fdPVR\">\u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng MP4 ho\u1eb7c MOV<\/strong>\u00a0.\u00a0Khi b\u1ea1n t\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng video gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb Animoto, n\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"Label-module--label--3mPBJ Label-module--spacing--2eZ0x\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cat_ghep_am_nhac\"><\/span>C\u1eaft gh\u00e9p \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a quen v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a YouTube. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u1ea1n \u0111ang tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 c\u00e1c quy t\u1eafc c\u1ee7a YouTube, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, mua nh\u1ea1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ph\u00e9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u1eb7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1ea1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ph\u00e9p t\u1eeb tr\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda video tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn <span class=\"BaseButton-module--fullWidth--1g5Gb\">nh\u01b0 A<\/span><span class=\"BaseButton-module--fullWidth--1g5Gb\">nimoto<\/span>\u00a0.<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"SectionTitle-module--sectionTitle--3wG12 SectionTitle-module--spacing--23XyU\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Phan_tao_phan_gioi_thieu_ve_YouTube_nen_dai_bao_lau\"><\/span>Ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 YouTube n\u00ean d\u00e0i bao l\u00e2u?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">Ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube ph\u1ea3i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00fang tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0i t\u1eeb n\u0103m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e2y. \u0110o\u1ea1n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean YouTube ph\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1ed9i dung ch\u00ednh.<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"SectionTitle-module--sectionTitle--3wG12 SectionTitle-module--spacing--23XyU\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cac_vi_du_gioi_thieu_tren_YouTube_de_truyen_cam_hung_cho_ban\"><\/span>C\u00e1c v\u00ed d\u1ee5 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean YouTube \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho b\u1ea1n<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">TED l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u00eanh YouTube n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd.\u00a0M\u1ed7i video tr\u00ean YouTube c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3\u00a0<span class=\"BaseButton-module--fullWidth--1g5Gb\">\u201cA Seat at the Table\u201d kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p cho b\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eb3ng gi\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Lilly Singh<\/span> \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i trong v\u00e0i gi\u00e2y. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9a bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0ng ho\u1ea1t h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd k\u00e8m theo hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng \u00e2m thanh \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng . Nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 n\u00e0y k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn.<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"SectionTitle-module--sectionTitle--3wG12 SectionTitle-module--spacing--23XyU\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ban_da_san_sang_tao_phan_gioi_thieu_tren_YouTube_chua\"><\/span>B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean YouTube ch\u01b0a?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">B\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o video gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean YouTube phong c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn?\u00a0Kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn xa h\u01a1n;\u00a0Animoto \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y.\u00a0Animoto s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c video gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean YouTube c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u00f4ng th\u1eadt chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.\u00a0B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u YouTube c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang b\u1ea1n ngay h\u00f4m nay.<\/p>\n<div class=\"Paragraph-module--paragraph--1jQPg Paragraph-module--spacing--DUXZG\">\n<div class=\"s-player-wrapper EmbedVideoPlayer-module--playerWrapper--_H6iG EmbedVideoPlayer-module--defaultPosition--1EpX6\">\n<div class=\"EmbedVideoPlayer-module--player--21RBa\">\n<div class=\"react-player__preview\">\n<div class=\"react-player__shadow\">\u00a0\u0110\u1ecdc th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/youtube-shorts-chien-luoc-ki-thuat-so.html\/\">Youtube Shorts chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t k\u0129 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1<\/a><\/div>\n<div><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/10-cong-cu-manh-me-de-cai-thien-su-hien.html\/\">10 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n tr\u00ean Youtube<\/a><\/div>\n<div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 YouTube 